---
// French mentions légales page (LEGAL-01): site publisher identity, hosting
// provider, and business status, per LCEN Article 1-1 (current text,
// effective 2024-05-23 — this article was renumbered by the SREN law from
// its long-standing pre-2024 citation; do not cite the old, abolished
// numbering here, 04-RESEARCH.md Pitfall 2).
//
// Hardcoded content (Pattern 3 — no Sanity fetch), same convention as
// src/pages/about.astro: legal copy needs developer review before any
// change, so it is not CMS-editable (04-RESEARCH.md "Don't Hand-Roll").
//
// Identity disclosure (D-08, RESOLVED): LCEN Article 1-1, I requires a
// professional editorial site to disclose the publisher's real legal name,
// not just a trade/brand name — "Romane Lepont, exerçant sous le nom
// commercial « Atelier Jacqueline Suzanne »".
//
// Address/phone (D-09, RESOLVED): Romane has no professional address or
// phone line on file yet. Shipped as explicit, clearly-marked `.placeholder`
// pending fields — never fabricated, never silently omitted.
//
// Hosting (D-07): names OVH as the confirmed Phase-5 end-state host, even
// though the site is still actually live on GitHub Pages today. Address/RCS/
// APE details verified directly against OVH's own live mentions-légales page
// (ovhcloud.com/fr/terms-and-conditions/) during this task — that page does
// not itself publish a phone number for OVH SAS, so none is asserted here
// (04-RESEARCH.md Assumption A2 delta, recorded in 04-01-SUMMARY.md).
//
// Business status (D-10, RESOLVED): Romane has not filed any business
// registration — her activity is occasional and, by her own account, below
// the threshold that would trigger a registration obligation. This is NOT
// the "SIRET en cours d'attribution" (filed, pending issuance) case.
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mentions légales — Atelier Jacqueline Suzanne">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Mentions légales</h1>

    <h2>Éditeur du site</h2>
    <p>Romane Lepont, exerçant sous le nom commercial « Atelier Jacqueline Suzanne ».</p>
    <p>Directeur de la publication : Romane Lepont.</p>
    <p>E-mail : contact@atelierjacquelinesuzanne.fr</p>
    <p class="placeholder">Adresse : à compléter.</p>
    <p class="placeholder">Téléphone : à compléter.</p>

    <h2>Hébergement</h2>
    <p>
      OVH SAS — RCS Lille Métropole 424 761 419 00045 — Code APE 2620Z. Siège social : 2 rue
      Kellermann, 59100 Roubaix, France.
    </p>

    <h2>Statut</h2>
    <p class="placeholder">
      Statut : activité individuelle, non immatriculée — activité occasionnelle en dessous du
      seuil imposant l'immatriculation.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md);
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-display-size); /* Display role */
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .legal-page h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-heading-size); /* Heading role */
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .legal-page p {
    font-size: var(--text-body-size); /* Body role */
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .legal-page .placeholder {
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
